[
  {
    "startTime": 0.15,
    "endTime": 0.9500000000000001,
    "text": "Kobe!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 0.95,
    "endTime": 1.6,
    "text": "Hi."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1.6,
    "endTime": 1.81,
    "text": "What's happenin'?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1.81,
    "endTime": 3.3,
    "text": "What's happenin' with you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 3.3,
    "endTime": 4.5,
    "text": "Ah, just chillin'."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 4.5,
    "endTime": 6.269,
    "text": "Mr. Oscar Winner, congratulations, you"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.269,
    "endTime": 6.863,
    "text": "won an Oscar!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.863,
    "endTime": 7.946000000000001,
    "text": "Oh, thank you, thank you--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.946,
    "endTime": 8.737,
    "text": "[AUDIENCE CHEERING]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8.737,
    "endTime": 9.383000000000001,
    "text": "--thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.383,
    "endTime": 10.799,
    "text": "You're like an overachiever."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.8,
    "endTime": 11.3,
    "text": "[laughing]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.3,
    "endTime": 12.33,
    "text": "That's crazy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.33,
    "endTime": 13.4,
    "text": "I mean, it is amazing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.4,
    "endTime": 13.725,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.725,
    "endTime": 14.78,
    "text": "I mean, that's-- that's--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.78,
    "endTime": 15.466,
    "text": "congratulations."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.466,
    "endTime": 15.966,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.966,
    "endTime": 17.439,
    "text": "Now what're you gonna go after?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.44,
    "endTime": 20.951,
    "text": "Uh, you know, just tryin' not to get on my wife's nerves at home"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.951,
    "endTime": 21.45,
    "text": "too much."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.45,
    "endTime": 22.189,
    "text": "I see, yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.19,
    "endTime": 23.44,
    "text": "You know, tryin' to stay busy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.44,
    "endTime": 25.43,
    "text": "Tryin' to stay busy, that's what it is, yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.43,
    "endTime": 27.689,
    "text": "So you turned 40 recently, right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.69,
    "endTime": 28.19,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.19,
    "endTime": 29.71,
    "text": "What did you do?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.71,
    "endTime": 32.99,
    "text": "Well, so, you know, I like working."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.98,
    "endTime": 32.598,
    "text": "Mm-hm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.598,
    "endTime": 33.513999999999996,
    "text": "You like working, too."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.515,
    "endTime": 35.36,
    "text": "We love working, and so I thought"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.36,
    "endTime": 38.39,
    "text": "I was flying down to LA from Orange County"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.39,
    "endTime": 39.566,
    "text": "to do some work on a show."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.566,
    "endTime": 40.660000000000004,
    "text": "Mm-hm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.66,
    "endTime": 43.4,
    "text": "I show up to the airport, my wife's there,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.4,
    "endTime": 45.589,
    "text": "our three daughters are there, the dog's there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.59,
    "endTime": 46.766000000000005,
    "text": "[audience laughing]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.766,
    "endTime": 48.57,
    "text": "And I'm lookin' at them like, what're you guys doin' here?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.57,
    "endTime": 49.944,
    "text": "They said, we're going to Mexico!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.944,
    "endTime": 51.319,
    "text": "And I'm like, oh, well, have fun."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.319,
    "endTime": 52.11,
    "text": "[audience laughing]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.11,
    "endTime": 53.55,
    "text": "No, idiot, you're comin' too!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.55,
    "endTime": 55.839999999999996,
    "text": "We're like, we're surprising you with a trip to Mexico!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.841,
    "endTime": 57.271,
    "text": "I was like, oh, awesome, cool."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.271,
    "endTime": 57.77,
    "text": "Wow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.77,
    "endTime": 58.900000000000006,
    "text": "Cool."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.9,
    "endTime": 58.26,
    "text": "So you went--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.26,
    "endTime": 60.3,
    "text": "So I was pleasantly kidnapped for my birthday."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.3,
    "endTime": 60.339999999999996,
    "text": "Oh, that's--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.34,
    "endTime": 60.78,
    "text": "[audience laughing]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.78,
    "endTime": 61.61,
    "text": "It was awesome."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.61,
    "endTime": 62.48,
    "text": "That's wonderful."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.48,
    "endTime": 62.638999999999996,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.64,
    "endTime": 63.61,
    "text": "You had a good time?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.61,
    "endTime": 64.129,
    "text": "I did have a good time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.129,
    "endTime": 66.504,
    "text": "Are you able to-- some people don't like their birthdays,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.504,
    "endTime": 67.25,
    "text": "but you enjoy it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.25,
    "endTime": 68.69,
    "text": "No, I enjoyed it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.69,
    "endTime": 70.11,
    "text": "I mean, you know, just hanging out with the kids."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.11,
    "endTime": 72.95,
    "text": "Is it-- is it easy for you to sit still and relax?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.95,
    "endTime": 75.17,
    "text": "You said you like to work, but a lot of times people"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.17,
    "endTime": 77.285,
    "text": "like us don't know what to do on vacation."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.285,
    "endTime": 79.619,
    "text": "Yeah, if I sit still for too long I go a little crazy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.62,
    "endTime": 80.12,
    "text": "Right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.12,
    "endTime": 81.35000000000001,
    "text": "All right, so the--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.35,
    "endTime": 83.58999999999999,
    "text": "LeBron James is now with the Lakers."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.6,
    "endTime": 85.49,
    "text": "Rumors were that you were gonna come out of retirement"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.49,
    "endTime": 87.38,
    "text": "and play with him on the team."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.38,
    "endTime": 88.637,
    "text": "Yeah, I heard that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.637,
    "endTime": 90.7,
    "text": "[audience laughing]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.7,
    "endTime": 93.11500000000001,
    "text": "I actually heard that when I was in Mexico for my birthday."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.115,
    "endTime": 93.615,
    "text": "Uh-huh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.615,
    "endTime": 95.53,
    "text": "\"Kobe's training like crazy,\" I'm sayin', boy,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.53,
    "endTime": 96.47,
    "text": "I'm sittin' back with a margarita."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.47,
    "endTime": 97.53,
    "text": "What you talkin' about?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.53,
    "endTime": 97.995,
    "text": "[audience laughing]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.995,
    "endTime": 99.42,
    "text": "I don't know what kinda training y'all talkin' about."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.42,
    "endTime": 100.254,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.254,
    "endTime": 100.92,
    "text": "That's not true."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.92,
    "endTime": 101.4,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.4,
    "endTime": 101.73,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.73,
    "endTime": 102.33,
    "text": "God, no."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.33,
    "endTime": 103.41,
    "text": "No, never."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.41,
    "endTime": 103.95,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.95,
    "endTime": 104.67,
    "text": "Not a chance."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.67,
    "endTime": 105.28,
    "text": "You're done."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.28,
    "endTime": 105.97,
    "text": "Zip, zero."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.97,
    "endTime": 106.56,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.56,
    "endTime": 108.43,
    "text": "How often do you play basketball now?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.43,
    "endTime": 108.93,
    "text": "I don't."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.93,
    "endTime": 109.62,
    "text": "Really?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.62,
    "endTime": 110.52000000000001,
    "text": "My daughter plays--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.52,
    "endTime": 111.75,
    "text": "I know you coach her, right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.75,
    "endTime": 112.958,
    "text": "--yeah, my 12-year-old plays."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.958,
    "endTime": 115.85,
    "text": "Yeah, I coach her, and so, you know, she does all the playin'."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.85,
    "endTime": 117.0,
    "text": "And she tells you, she'll-- if like,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.0,
    "endTime": 117.93,
    "text": "she was here she'd tell you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.93,
    "endTime": 120.12,
    "text": "She'd go, yeah I'mma be a better basketball player than my dad."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.12,
    "endTime": 120.661,
    "text": "I'm doin' it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.661,
    "endTime": 122.59,
    "text": "Well, she's good, she's really good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.59,
    "endTime": 123.9,
    "text": "I mean--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.9,
    "endTime": 123.89,
    "text": "Yeah, she works."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.89,
    "endTime": 125.82000000000001,
    "text": "That would be-- first of all--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.82,
    "endTime": 127.809,
    "text": "She's really physical, too."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.81,
    "endTime": 128.729,
    "text": "I'm like, man--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.729,
    "endTime": 130.435,
    "text": "Look at her."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.435,
    "endTime": 131.28,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.28,
    "endTime": 132.78,
    "text": "Wow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.78,
    "endTime": 134.465,
    "text": "Yeah, so what's it like--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.465,
    "endTime": 135.9,
    "text": "[Kobe laughing]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.9,
    "endTime": 136.59,
    "text": "--that you're coaching her?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.59,
    "endTime": 138.39000000000001,
    "text": "Isn't that unfair that you--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.39,
    "endTime": 139.29,
    "text": "I mean, come on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.29,
    "endTime": 141.86599999999999,
    "text": "Like, that's like, really aggressive."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.866,
    "endTime": 144.24,
    "text": "But isn't that unfair that you're coaching your daughter?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.24,
    "endTime": 146.52,
    "text": "Like, what about--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.52,
    "endTime": 149.49,
    "text": "No, I mean, I think like, when we play opposing teams and--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.49,
    "endTime": 150.36,
    "text": "That's what I mean."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.36,
    "endTime": 152.68,
    "text": "--the coach comes up to me and he's like,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.68,
    "endTime": 153.241,
    "text": "hey, take it easy on us."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 153.241,
    "endTime": 155.49,
    "text": "I'm like, dude, I'm not out there shootin' jump shots."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.49,
    "endTime": 157.63,
    "text": "I can't control what these 12-year-olds do to you, man."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.63,
    "endTime": 158.269,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.27,
    "endTime": 161.10000000000002,
    "text": "But you're giving them the-- all the tricks of--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.1,
    "endTime": 161.76,
    "text": "No, I am."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.76,
    "endTime": 162.26,
    "text": "I am."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.26,
    "endTime": 165.72,
    "text": "So I started working with them a year ago,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 165.72,
    "endTime": 167.844,
    "text": "and you have the same group of girls,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.844,
    "endTime": 169.26,
    "text": "and we just work every single day."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.26,
    "endTime": 170.968,
    "text": "Like, they have goals of going to go play"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.968,
    "endTime": 173.47,
    "text": "at major universities, and they're really driven about it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.47,
    "endTime": 175.136,
    "text": "I say, listen, I can help you get there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.136,
    "endTime": 175.731,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.731,
    "endTime": 177.48,
    "text": "And we just work on all the little details"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.48,
    "endTime": 180.6,
    "text": "and they're really good, really, really smart,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.6,
    "endTime": 181.7,
    "text": "and very competitive."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.7,
    "endTime": 183.149,
    "text": "God, what lucky little girls."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.15,
    "endTime": 185.179,
    "text": "Can you imagine that Kobe Bryant is your coach?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.179,
    "endTime": 185.97,
    "text": "[AUDIENCE LAUGHING]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.97,
    "endTime": 187.292,
    "text": "That-- that's amazing--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 187.292,
    "endTime": 188.92,
    "text": "But hey, we practice every day, though."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.92,
    "endTime": 190.5,
    "text": "We practice every day, two hours."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.5,
    "endTime": 191.61,
    "text": "Yeah, well that's how you get there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 191.61,
    "endTime": 192.686,
    "text": "Right, that's what I say."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 192.686,
    "endTime": 195.6,
    "text": "Some parents are like, wait, you're practicing every day?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.6,
    "endTime": 195.29999999999998,
    "text": "Why?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.3,
    "endTime": 196.716,
    "text": "Shouldn't they have a normal life?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.716,
    "endTime": 198.72,
    "text": "Yeah, I mean, it's kinda-- it's normal to me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 198.72,
    "endTime": 198.99,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 198.99,
    "endTime": 199.781,
    "text": "[audience laughing]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.781,
    "endTime": 200.29,
    "text": "Yeah, yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.29,
    "endTime": 201.51,
    "text": "They'll be thanking 'em when those kids"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 201.51,
    "endTime": 202.334,
    "text": "buy 'em a house someday."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.335,
    "endTime": 202.65,
    "text": "[audience laughing]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.65,
    "endTime": 203.59,
    "text": "There you go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 203.59,
    "endTime": 205.79,
    "text": "They're gonna to be thanking you."
  }
]